      <h3>About</h3>
	  <p>
			Hi, I am a M.S. student in <a href="https://uilab.kr/">User & Information Lab (U&I Lab)</a>, KAIST. My research interests are in Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Human-Computer Interaction (HCI), especially in Automated Essay Scoring and English education.
	  </p>




